thenticity ratings for each match. Company insights: [Paste Research]. My resume: [Paste Resume].\n\n✉️ Prompt 6: Distinct Value Communicator\nWrite a compelling second paragraph showcasing my unique strengths for [Role]. Develop three versions emphasizing problem-solving, innovation, or team-building skills. Include measurable results and forward-looking statements. Rate differentiation level for each version. My resume: [Paste Resume]. Job description: [Paste Job Description].\n\n✉️ Prompt 7: Passion Statement Builder\nCraft an enthusiastic third paragraph expressing excitement about the opportunity at [Company Name]. Incorporate industry knowledge and company-specific insights. Create tailored versions for startups, corporate environments, or growth-stage businesses. Evaluate sincerity signals for each version. My resume: [Paste Resume]. Company insights: [Paste Research].\n\n👉 Follow me for more AI-powered career tips!\n\n🔄 Share this post to help others elevate their job applications!\n…more"
